{
    "AWSTemplateFormatVersion": "2010-09-09",
    "Description": "This template will deploy a Talend CI instance into an existing VPC subnet.  **WARNING** This template creates Amazon EC2 instance and related resources. You will be billed for the AWS resources used if you create a stack from this template. QS(9999)",
